Revision history for Perl extension Net::Frame::Layer::Syslog.

1.05 Tue Dec 13 17:48:36 EST 2016
   - Remove Socket dependence and make _getHost() return hostname.
   - Change in print() to print facility and severity numbers and only names 
     if they correspond to known values.
   - Change in print() to check if not defined content() for short print.
      - content(undef) in pack() to facilitate above.
   - Makefile.PL removed Socket::GetAddrInfo dependency.

1.04 Mon Nov 19 17:48:36 EST 2012
   - Socket name lookups now Socket version independent.

1.03 Mon Feb  3 17:48:36 EST 2012
   - Socket / Socket6 woes with getaddrinfo Perl 5.12 vs 5.14

1.02 Thu Jan 26 17:48:36 EST 2012
   - Windows + CPAN = withoutworldwriteables

1.01 Thu Jan 26 17:48:36 EST 2012
   - t\02 ... dubious test number corrected
   - 'use if' pragma Perl version < 5.014 for Socket6 in Syslog.pm

1.00 Wed Jan 13 17:48:36 EST 2012
   - first public release

